Description: Link checker for Hugo static sites
 A command-line tool to check for broken links in Hugo static sites.
 .
 Features:
  * Check internal and external links
  * Support for various output formats (text, JSON, HTML)
  * Configurable ignore patterns
  * Hugo-specific link checking logic
  * Support for checking images and other assets
